1
00:00:28,430 --> 00:00:30,830
Prime Minister, something terrible has happened!

2
00:00:30,830 --> 00:00:31,230
Speak.

3
00:00:31,700 --> 00:00:34,360
Our spies in the palace risked their lives to send a message.

4
00:00:34,360 --> 00:00:36,660
The hidden guards sent to Yanxi Palace were killed by a single needle to the throat,

5
00:00:36,660 --> 00:00:38,260
dying in Qu Jingzhi's bedchamber.

6
00:00:38,260 --> 00:00:40,430
Thirty top assassins outside the Shenwu Gate

7
00:00:40,430 --> 00:00:42,530
were all slashed to pieces by the Eastern Depot's Xiuchun swords.

8
00:00:42,530 --> 00:00:45,300
Ying Wujiu fought his way out of the palace with Qu Jingzhi,

9
00:00:45,300 --> 00:00:46,400
and their whereabouts are unknown.

10
00:00:46,400 --> 00:00:48,700
That bitch Qu Jingzhi killed my hidden guards!

11
00:00:48,700 --> 00:00:49,530
The secret letter!

12
00:00:49,530 --> 00:00:50,800
I gave it to the hidden guard

13
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:52,030
to force Qu Jingzhi to frame

14
00:00:52,030 --> 00:00:54,330
the Eastern Depot with that secret letter of treason. Where is it?

15
00:00:54,330 --> 00:00:57,200
There was nothing on the hidden guard's body.

16
00:00:58,630 --> 00:00:59,630
It's over.

17
00:00:59,730 --> 00:01:02,830
That letter contains the defense map I used to contact the Northern Di.

18
00:01:02,830 --> 00:01:05,260
That bitch bit me!

19
00:01:05,430 --> 00:01:08,300
She eloped with Ying Wujiu and the secret letter.

20
00:01:08,830 --> 00:01:10,000
We can't wait anymore.

21
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:10,730
Once it's dawn,

22
00:01:10,730 --> 00:01:12,530
if that eunuch dog hands the letter to the Emperor,

23
00:01:12,530 --> 00:01:14,590
my entire Yu family will be executed.

24
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:16,600
Pass on my order.

25
00:01:16,860 --> 00:01:18,660
Immediately mobilize all our private troops in the city

26
00:01:18,660 --> 00:01:20,300
to surround all major city gates.

27
00:01:20,300 --> 00:01:22,460
Even if you have to turn the capital upside down,

28
00:01:22,460 --> 00:01:24,990
you must chop those two brats into mincemeat!

29
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:29,930
My lady.

30
00:01:30,930 --> 00:01:32,860
The Emperor's headache has flared up again.

31
00:01:32,860 --> 00:01:34,259
He is smashing things in pain.

32
00:01:34,259 --> 00:01:38,460
Please hurry to the Hall of Mental Cultivation to administer acupuncture.

33
00:01:38,729 --> 00:01:39,300
My lady.

34
00:01:39,860 --> 00:01:41,300
I am coming in.

35
00:01:56,729 --> 00:01:59,500
Ah!

36
00:02:01,930 --> 00:02:04,260
Somebody! Come quickly!

37
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:05,860
The lady is gone!

38
00:02:05,900 --> 00:02:07,530
Assassins!

39
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:09,500
Your Majesty.

40
00:02:09,500 --> 00:02:10,300
Outside the Shenwu Gate,

41
00:02:10,300 --> 00:02:13,030
dozens of corpses of the Yu family's hidden guards were found.

42
00:02:13,030 --> 00:02:13,890
All of them were

43
00:02:14,030 --> 00:02:16,900
killed by a single strike from the Eastern Depot's Xiuchun swords.

44
00:02:16,900 --> 00:02:19,460
The Director and Miss Qu are missing.

45
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,800
Ying Wujiu!

46
00:02:26,030 --> 00:02:27,730
You liar!

47
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,460
You crippled slave,

48
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,730
how dare you elope with my woman!

49
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,200
Ah!

50
00:02:39,430 --> 00:02:41,360
Seal the nine gates of the capital!

51
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,400
Dig three feet into the ground

52
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,430
and bring them back to me!

53
00:02:44,430 --> 00:02:45,530
I want them alive,

54
00:02:45,530 --> 00:02:46,130
or if dead,

55
00:02:46,160 --> 00:02:47,829
I will flay them myself!

56
00:02:53,860 --> 00:02:54,660
Jingzhi.

57
00:02:55,660 --> 00:02:57,030
When Helan Ci finds you missing,

58
00:02:57,030 --> 00:02:58,230
he will surely go mad.

59
00:02:58,500 --> 00:02:59,360
He must have

60
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:01,200
already sealed the nine gates of the capital.

61
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:02,300
I will gather all

62
00:03:02,300 --> 00:03:03,800
the Eastern Depot's hidden agents in the city.

63
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:06,230
Even if it costs the last man in the Eastern Depot,

64
00:03:06,230 --> 00:03:08,130
I will surely send you out of the city.

65
00:03:08,130 --> 00:03:08,990
Out of the city?

66
00:03:12,700 --> 00:03:13,830
Why should we run?

67
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:15,060
Ying Wujiu.

68
00:03:15,830 --> 00:03:17,200
Since this secret letter of treason

69
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,329
is in our hands,

70
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:20,430
the one who shouldn't be able to sleep now

71
00:03:20,430 --> 00:03:21,760
is Yu Henian.

72
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,560
Ah!

73
00:03:31,460 --> 00:03:32,460
Why wasn't the secret letter

74
00:03:32,460 --> 00:03:34,760
sent back to the army immediately?

75
00:03:35,230 --> 00:03:37,130
How do you do things?

76
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:40,200
If you can't get the secret letter back,

77
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:42,400
Then you don't need to live in this world anymore.

78
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:44,560
My Lord, that bitch ran away.

79
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,829
Find that bitch for me.

80
00:03:47,260 --> 00:03:49,460
We can't let that secret letter be lost.

81
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,130
Dead or alive.

82
00:04:04,100 --> 00:04:04,900
Ah!

83
00:04:05,700 --> 00:04:06,500
Ying Wujiu,

84
00:04:06,900 --> 00:04:07,660
it's you.

85
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,160
You eunuch dog!

86
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:12,530
How dare you collude with the Emperor's woman to defect!

87
00:04:14,730 --> 00:04:15,530
Eunuch dog!

88
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,029
Yu Henian.

89
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,130
Save your breath

90
00:04:19,630 --> 00:04:21,730
and say it in the underworld.

91
00:04:29,900 --> 00:04:30,700
Ah!

92
00:04:34,930 --> 00:04:35,659
Yu Henian.

93
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:38,500
This knife you sharpened yourself

94
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:40,460
didn't stab the Governor,

95
00:04:40,930 --> 00:04:41,730
but took the lives

96
00:04:41,730 --> 00:04:43,130
of your entire Yu family.

97
00:04:44,900 --> 00:04:45,360
Report!

98
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:49,400
The Emperor has led 3,000 Imperial Guards to surround the teahouse.

99
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:56,860
Since the Emperor is here,

100
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,200
I will not accompany you to your deaths.

101
00:05:14,430 --> 00:05:15,230
Jingzhi.

102
00:05:15,930 --> 00:05:17,460
Even if you want to run away,

103
00:05:17,460 --> 00:05:19,330
why are you wearing his clothes?

104
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,630
I offered the whole world to you,

105
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:23,060
but you'd rather have a...

106
00:05:23,060 --> 00:05:24,860
a defective eunuch!
